description: Welcome to Elegant and Tastefully remodeled Penthouse in one of the most cared for buildings on a gorgeous walk street of Marina Peninsula and only steps to the sand. Enjoy the morning sun and ocean breeze through Panoramic glass windows throughout and on the lovely rooftop deck. Soaring ceiling, beautiful stonework with fireplace in a great and full of natural light living room. The bright and open dining room leads to a gorgeous kitchen with stainless appliances. The second bedroom is very spacious with walk-in closet and en suit full bath with an oversized soaking tub. This Stunning retreat is coastal living at its very best! Photos will follow.

Storybook Charmer! With its picturesque style, warm accents & whimsical details, you'll fall in love the moment you lay eyes on it. Distinctive & extensively remodeled from top-to-bottom blending Tudor-Esque elements w/ modern niceties, enhanced by a wood-burning fireplace & an asymmetrical roof. There's so much to like with its welcoming feel & easy flow from room-to-room. Gourmand chef's kitchen takes center stage w/ a thoughtful island that functions as well as entertains. Sleep tight in your master w/ its calm vibe thanks to the view of your melodious backyard. Reserved outdoor spaces create a natural context embracing the experience of living outdoors. For the pies de resistance, detached office-playroom w/ a private staircase leading to additional space, perfect for an afternoon nap after a dunk in your outdoor soaking hot tub. Ideally located in a family-friendly neighborhood, close to everything the west side offers. Indeed, this is the house you'll want to call home!
This 1895 square foot multi family home has 1 bedrooms and 2.0 bathrooms. It is located at 2513 Lincoln Blvd Venice, California.

Live At The Beach in This Magical Zen-Like Town Home  Steps From The Sand. This Four Level Beach Paradise Is A Corner Unit With Gorgeous Trees  and Ocean Views!   This Home Has Amazing Light and Feels Like A Single Family.  The Top Level and Roof Top Deck Have Ocean and Canal Views.  First Level Is The Large Master Bedroom With A New Luxurious Master Bath and Large Balcony With Steps To The Tropical Garden. Second Level Is The Open Living /Dining and Kitchen Area With New Skylights That Almost Span The Entire Living Room. There Is Also A Large Balcony Off Of The Living Room.  Third Level Is The Loft / Second Bedroom With A Full Bath and Closet. There Are Two Side By Side Parking Spots in Gated Garage With Built in Storage Closets. This Is A Well- Maintained 8 Unit Building All Owner Occupied. Many Upgrades and Totally Renovated. Vacant and Easy To View Or I Am Happy To Do A Face Time Tour.
